query: SELECT TRD.WRKFLW_ID, TRD.SCRTY_SK, SCRTY.TCKR_SYM_ID, SCRTY.CUSIP_ID, SCRTY.SCRTY_DS, TRD.PRNCL_AM, TRD.CMSN_AM, TRN.TRANS_TYPE_DS BUY_SELL_DS, TRD.EXCTN_PR, TRD.GRSS_AM, TRD.TRANS_QT, TRD.MARK_UP_DOWN_AM, TRD.TTL_FEES_AM, TRD.SALES_CNSSN_AM, TRD.TTL_CMSN_AM, TRD.TTL_CMSN_PCG, TRD.TTL_CHRGS_AM, TRD.TTL_CHRGS_PCG, ASST.ASSET_TYPE_SK, ASST.ASSET_TYPE_DS, TRD.ACCNT_SK, ACCT.ACCNT_NB, ACCT.ACCNT_NB_KEY, ACCT.MSKD_ACCNT_NB, CLNDR.CLNDR_DT, CLDR.CLNDR_DT STLMT_DT, TRD.REP_SK, REP.INTNL_INDVL_DSPLY_NM, REP.INDVL_CRD_NB, 'Y' AS REP_TYPE, REP.SPLIT_REP_FL, TRD.BRNCH_SK, BRNCH.INTNL_BRNCH_ID, SOL.SOLCT_TYPE_SK, SOL.SOLCT_TYPE_DS, CPCTY.TRANS_CPCTY_SK, CPCTY.TRANS_CPCTY_DS, TRD_TYPE.TRD_TYPE_SK, TRD_TYPE.TRD_TYPE_DS, TRD.ACCNT_TYPE_SK, ACCNT_TYPE.ACCNT_TYPE_DS, ACCNT_TYPE.EMP_ACCTN_FL, 'Y' AS WTCH_LIST_SCRTY_FL, TRD.TRD_CTGRY_SK, CASE WHEN TRD.TRD_CTGRY_SK IN (1,3) THEN 'Y' WHEN TRD.TRD_CTGRY_SK = 2 THEN 'N' END AS NTTD_TRD_FL, TRD.PS_RFRNC_NB, TRD.TRD_SERIAL_NB, 0 AS CHRG_OVR_CMSN_PCG, TRD.EXCTN_TM, TRD.CRNCY_CD FROM AW_ANLYTS.TRD_FT TRD LEFT OUTER JOIN AW_ANLYTS.ACCNT_DM ACCT ON trd.wrkflw_id = acct.wrkflw_id and TRD.ACCNT_SK = ACCT.ACCNT_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW_ANLYTS.ASSET_TYPE_DM ASST ON trd.wrkflw_id = ASST.wrkflw_id and TRD.ASSET_TYPE_SK = ASST.ASSET_TYPE_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW_ANLYTS.SCRTY_DM SCRTY ON trd.wrkflw_id = SCRTY.wrkflw_id and TRD.SCRTY_SK = SCRTY.SCRTY_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW_ANLYTS.REP_DM REP ON trd.wrkflw_id = REP.wrkflw_id and TRD.REP_SK = REP.REP_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW_ANLYTS.BRNCH_DM BRNCH ON trd.wrkflw_id = BRNCH.wrkflw_id and TRD.BRNCH_SK = BRNCH.BRNCH_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW_ANLYTS.SOLCT_TYPE_DM SOL ON TRD.SOLCT_TYPE_SK = SOL.SOLCT_TYPE_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW_ANLYTS.TRANS_TYPE_DM TRN ON TRD.TRANS_TYPE_SK = TRN.TRANS_TYPE_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW_ANLYTS.TRANS_CPCTY_DM CPCTY ON TRD.TRANS_CPCTY_SK = CPCTY.TRANS_CPCTY_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW_ANLYTS.TRD_TYPE_DM TRD_TYPE ON TRD.TRD_TYPE_SK = TRD_TYPE.TRD_TYPE_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW_ANLYTS.ACCNT_TYPE_DM ACCNT_TYPE ON TRD.ACCNT_TYPE_SK = ACCNT_TYPE.ACCNT_TYPE_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW.CLNDR_DM CLNDR ON TRD.ASOF_CLNDR_SK = CLNDR.CLNDR_SK LEFT OUTER JOIN AW.CLNDR_DM CLDR ON TRD.STLMT_CLNDR_SK = CLDR.CLNDR_SK and trd.wrkflw_id = 200 and trd.accnt_sk = 3819028 and trd.rep_sk = 4499 order by prncl_am limit 500

assignments.expr_158: (CASE WHEN ("trd_ctgry_sk" IN (1, 3)) THEN 'Y' WHEN ("trd_ctgry_sk" = 2) THEN 'N' END)
